### Escrow Transactions API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Variables
@bookingId = 1
@milestoneId = 1
@transactionId = 1

### 1. Create Escrow Transaction (Deposit)
POST {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": {{bookingId}},
  "transaction_type": "deposit",
  "amount": 10000.00,
  "currency_id": 1,
  "notes": "Initial deposit for booking"
}

### 2. List Escrow Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. List Escrow Transactions by Booking
GET {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/booking/{{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Escrow Transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Release Escrow to Provider
POST {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/release
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "milestone_id": {{milestoneId}},
  "amount": 1800.00,
  "released_to": 2,
  "release_method": "bank_transfer",
  "reference_number": "REF123456",
  "notes": "Milestone 1 payment release"
}

### 6. Process Refund
POST {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": {{bookingId}},
  "amount": 5000.00,
  "currency_id": 1,
  "notes": "Partial refund for cancellation"
}

### 7. Hold Funds for Dispute
POST {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/dispute/hold
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": {{bookingId}},
  "amount": 10000.00,
  "currency_id": 1,
  "notes": "Dispute hold pending resolution"
}

### 8. Release Funds from Dispute
POST {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/dispute/release
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": {{bookingId}},
  "amount": 10000.00,
  "currency_id": 1,
  "released_to": 1,
  "notes": "Dispute resolved, releasing funds to customer"
}

### 9. Update Escrow Transaction
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "reference_number": "REF789012",
  "notes": "Transaction processed successfully"
}

### 10. Filter by Transaction Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions?transaction_type=release&booking_id={{bookingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/escrow-transactions?status=completed&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



